l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wto1665702974164.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wto1665702974164.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wto1665702974164.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wto1665702974164\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                             \n Create Tables for Modeled Entities\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The suffix used in modeled entity names can be used to group entities into a logical group.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"wto1665702974164__context_w3903ab1b5b1_w3904ab1b5_w3905ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"wto1665702974164__topic_d61292e1_d61293e1_d61294e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wto1665702974164__p_d61295e1_d61296e1_d61297e1\">For each group of entities:</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26918e1_d26919e1_d26920e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run the Create Table facility (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/genSql</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">createtable</code>) to generate SQL scripts to create the necessary tables, indexes and stored procedures. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cck1665702542032.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cck1665702542032.html\" title=\"The /genSql switch generates DBMS-specific SQL command scripts for preparing an application database or the Uniface Repository, including creating tables and enforcing referential integrity constraints in the database.\">/genSql</a>.\n                              </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26921e1_d26922e1_d26923e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">If you want Sybase to handle referential integrity instead of Uniface:\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26924e1_d26925e1_d26926e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"wto1665702974164__p_d61298e1_d61299e1_d61300e1\">Set the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">dbms ri</span> connector option in the application assignment file.\n These scripts enable your application to:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26927e1_d26928e1_d26929e1\">Enforce declarative referential integrity constraints and database triggers.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26930e1_d26931e1_d26932e1\">Drop declarative referential integrity constraints and database triggers.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26933e1_d26934e1_d26935e1\">Check relationships in the database for violations of referential integrity.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26936e1_d26937e1_d26938e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"wto1665702974164__p_d61301e1_d61302e1_d61303e1\">Add the following to the SQL scripts produced by the Create Script facility:\n <var class=\"keyword varname\">DatabaseName</var>is the database in which the models will be created.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">use <var class=\"keyword varname\">DatabaseName</var>\ngo</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26939e1_d26940e1_d26941e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"wto1665702974164__p_d61304e1_d61305e1_d61306e1\">Execute the SQL script to enforce referential integrity constraints in DBMS.\n These files should be created for all relationships. Even if the model entities do not include a relationship, referential integrity controls may be required for an overflow table.</span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"wto1665702974164__li_d26942e1_d26943e1_d26944e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run the <span class=\"ph filepath\">syb4xext.sql</span> script in all databases in which stored procedures are used. This script creates the generic table existence procedure <code class=\"ph codeph\">U4_EXIST_CHECK</code>.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ovd1665702964846.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>dbms ri</a><p>Enable Sybase referential integrity controls.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533526\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533526\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Create Tables for Modeled Entities Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Create Tables for Modeled Entities The suffix used in modeled entity names can be used to group entities into a logical group. For each group of entities: Run the Create Table facility ( /genSql createtable ) to generate SQL scripts to create the necessary tables, indexes and stored procedures. For more information, see /genSql . If you want Sybase to handle referential integrity instead of Uniface: Set the dbms ri connector option in the application assignment file. These scripts enable your application to: Enforce declarative referential integrity constraints and database triggers. Drop declarative referential integrity constraints and database triggers. Check relationships in the database for violations of referential integrity. Add the following to the SQL scripts produced by the Create Script facility: DatabaseName is the database in which the models will be created. use DatabaseName go Copy Execute the SQL script to enforce referential integrity constraints in DBMS. These files should be created for all relationships. Even if the model entities do not include a relationship, referential integrity controls may be required for an overflow table. Run the syb4xext.sql script in all databases in which stored procedures are used. This script creates the generic table existence procedure U4_EXIST_CHECK . Related Links dbms ri Enable Sybase referential integrity controls. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}